Program: Outlook
Title: 15/05/2012
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00rg2k7
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 16 May 2012
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, Kim Hee Tae, the man who risks his life and liberty to rescue orphans who have fled from North Korea into China. Also, the Spaniard who lost his job in construction and went back to his roots in farming; and doing the rounds with one of New York's few remaining "seltzer men," who deliver fizzy water door to door. Show less